    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... it doesn't feel like a defense. it feels like the truth. like the person everyone knows is just a hollow shell and there's nothing left inside to actually \"protect.\" how am i supposed to keep performing a role when there's no one even home to play it?",
